Description: The code that a participant is assigned to. E.g., OAS2_0001.
The code that describes the MR session. E.g., OAS2_0001_MR1.
Describes the Alzheimer state of the participant at the moment of the scan session. Either Demented or Nondemented.
Corresponds with MRI ID. E.g., visit = 3.
Contains the images in the form of a numpy array.
Every cropped picture has its own column, it contains a certain voxel space of the full sized images, also in numpy array format.
